OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772204159
OL,3,CMet Police officer who stole #2.25
OL,4,Ctuna baguette 'would have been sacked'
OL,6,FA Metropolitan Police officer who
OL,7,Fstole a #2.25 tuna baguette from Pret
OL,8,FA Manger would have been sacked if he
OL,9,Fhad not left the force, a misconduct
OL,10,Fpanel has found.
OL,12,FFormer Pc David Fyfe was filmed on
OL,13,FCCTV taking the sandwich whilst on
OL,14,Fduty on April 9 last year from a Pret
OL,15,Fin Wood Green shopping mall in north
OL,16,FLondon.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
