PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772204159
OL,3,CMet Police officer who stole #2.25
OL,4,Ctuna baguette 'would have been sacked'
OL,6,FThe ruling said the panel noted that a
OL,7,F"uniformed officer shoplifting in
OL,8,Fplain sight was reprehensible
OL,9,Fbehaviour".
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@JO]
